/KASHIR HASHIRIM //PR

/XXTHE SONG OF SONGS/PR

/ITSelect from among the following:/PR

/PR

The Song of Songs, ascribed to Solomon./PR

/PR

He kisses me, full kisses with his mouth./PR

Yes, better is your love than wine, [I say,]/PR

Oh, the aroma of your balm!/PR

--a balsamum poured out: your name!/PR

For such a thing the young girls love you./PR

Take me along with you, letòs run!/PR

/PR

